Python 3.3 and 3.4 is EOL (https://devguide.python.org/#status-of-python-branches),
added more recent python versions (3.6, 3.7, 3.8).

commit.message:
Coverage support param `--concurrency.
Fix travis, support py 3.5
disable coveralls badge. wrong coverage info.
rename module `pypi` to package. FIX manifest creation for setuptools.
do not install pathlib on python3.4
travis: install hunspell before running tests
coverage: support coverage of single modules
added doit task to auto update version on doc/config and pkg/__init__.py
fix docs & use new pythonhosted url

pyflakes: consider 'unicode' a builtin even on py3 to support code
compatible with both py2 and py3.
move Config class out of doitpy package
